<h1>Comments</h1>
<div style="width:90%; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; margin-top:10px; background-color:#FFFFFF; border-radius:5px; border: black 1px solid;" >
	<p style="text-align:center;">
		This is just a placeholder page for comments. I assume that eventually there will be a place to add them when viewing an article.
	</p>
</div>
<div style="width:90%; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; margin-top:20px;">
	<table style="margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto">
		<tr >
			<td><%= button_to "Add Comment", :action => "add", :method => :get  %></td>
			<td><%= button_to "Delete Comment", "comments/delete", :method => :get  %></td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</div>